    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    ClientStatusInfo
    JavaFX-compatible model class representing the connection status of a client.
    DBController
    Handles all direct access to the database.
    NotificationController
    Controller responsible for sending notifications to customers.
    ReportController
    Controller responsible for generating and retrieving restaurant reports.
    ReservationController
    Business logic controller for all reservation-related operations.
    RestaurantManagementController
    Controller responsible for managing restaurant configuration settings.
    Server
    Main class that extends AbstractServer OCSF server class that handles client communication, interacts with the database controller, and updates the JavaFX GUI via ServerUI.
    ServerFrameController
    JavaFX controller for the server configuration and monitoring GUI.
    ServerMain_Gui
    Main entry point for the server-side JavaFX graphical user interface.
    ServerUI
    Interface for sending messages and client connection updates to the server GUI.
    UserAccountController
    Controller responsible for user account management operations.
